緊份文職工作(非金融保險)，朝9晚5。感覺文職工作幾好，都想繼續發展<br />\n<br />\n但而家香港搵工\\轉工 都要睇cert，我應該繼續番工到25歲用年長生報ou上大學，定到下年8月再報番ive hd 再駁topup?<br />\n<br />\n想問各位巴打有冇類似經驗?<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒巴打們</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主同你差唔多，不過我讀完fd就無讀，之後返過幾份炒散，人生無方向，連自己都唔知想點，好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5cefe669a02284f69189fa187341d6b65b06f8","tid":10771,"uid":38630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:40:15.000Z","msg":"人生交叉點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc763475aa763147e95471b726ebb2bf36866836","tid":10771,"uid":36770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:49:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依家讀緊yr1 hd，難到想喊，下年唔知retake定出黎做野好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打本身讀咩科? 好迷惘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 20歲又唔細又大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n讀緊航空，上堂完全聽唔明，自己係毅進升上黎，英文底差<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔想咁快出黎做野，進退兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  可能試下retake下年睇下讀唔讀得黎，如果都係唔得就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f18d2797217d70f400c9a4dd925e7045b7bf6c1","tid":10771,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"文職可以有咩發展<br />\n咪玩<br />\n打下字覆下email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff925f3ea3eb7b4ab862f705d805d6c4aade45","tid":10771,"uid":38837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:58:45.000Z","msg":"翻工啦 大學生讀完岀黎都搵唔到工啦 何必再用多d錢去拎個無用既cert 早d翻工拎下經驗好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b6e7200e1293c34f9a259