/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一係就做d唔洗指定學歷嘅，一係就手藝<br />\n讀番書啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係過來人，dse大炒，出黎做左兩年野<br />\n發覺冇學歷真係唔撚掂<br />\n而家讀緊M.E HD</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打 我認同 最緊要要知道想從事邊行 之後讀果課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5fcbe432bd9a5ae9e12431f52d866ebfbf1a54c","tid":10771,"uid":3172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:35:35.000Z","msg":"垃圾  hd都1.幾  你都係唔好諗讀書"},{"pid":"a904c45b3586b079f03c627c6191291926ecacc1","tid":10771,"uid":18268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:40:45.000Z","msg":"半工讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日頭返工夜晚返學"},{"pid":"08959c54f4829067d5eb8a16655da077a60d6954","tid":10771,"uid":2569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:51:18.000Z","msg":"讀書，自己覺得第時想讀都好難有心機有時間，讀書要親年輕"},{"pid":"8729cf368ed927a48f46a0aeb23596a41b903d2f","tid":10771,"uid":4697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"中六畢業 工程撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44161f27077aad61a7db6c2426ee658eb548ba66","tid":10771,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"我今年廿一, 有張hd(社科) 係手, 畢業有fd 介紹入左間電腦公司做, 比人派左去間銀行做it 狗, 做左年半比格黎dpt 呀頭睇中, 肯比我冇經驗冇學歷都同我簽約, 仲要係做compliance  , 覺得自己好好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出黎做野唔係問題, 但真係平時要做好自己, 機會隨時都黎, 分分鐘比老闆睇中有位上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2b51e756b6d37658deb7ca19904e3f1fb3de79","tid":10771,"uid":18281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果你真係想係文職呢方面發展 建議你都係要讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  part time 