同心智都會有所改變。"},{"pid":"bf0557a734fe2a353bec4a2caa2b2bc357f61424","tid":10771,"uid":38465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:21:22.000Z","msg":"好多巴打留言認真留言，真係好多謝晒咁多位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗自己下年都會讀番書，正如咁多位巴打講有書襯早讀，不過讀咩都要諗下 唔想又浪費錢同時間<br />\n<br />\n仲有希望其他同我處境一樣既巴打都努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7908633d23b6f9f86f3f45fe337ddfe580adf7","tid":10771,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"FD上HD都只係得GPA 1.幾<br />\n咁你仲諗讀書呢條路？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7eba1fd3818cc14f65af8cd9df417affb517db","tid":10771,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:28:52.000Z","msg":"講真 搵到目標真係早D讀書好 <br />\n仲要係full time <br />\n遲下半工讀 好辛苦架<br />\n壓力大到自己頂唔順"},{"pid":"2a0497e915cbfae92e0532da0b7c767ccacb6005","tid":10771,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:29:01.000Z","msg":"做多一兩年野再讀書都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做耐左野個心態會唔同左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda0950a3c1eac4b8bb6169ff1dc560be2cf3e35","tid":10771,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做文職真係無前途 就算你跳槽做嚟做去都只係呢份人工呢個位<br />\n講得好聽就叫文職 其實咪又係打雜<br />\n巴打搵啲pt讀返書喇 有些少學歷到時轉工都易搵啲好公司<br />\n利申過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪係所謂文職咪又係打雜<br />\n比人點到仆街"}]}